5:1 Bukeye rubanda rw'Abayuda n'abagore babo baritotomba cyane, barega bene wabo b'Abayuda
5:2 kuko bamwe bavugaga bati “Abahungu bacu n'abakobwa bacu turi benshi, reka tujye kwihahira tubone ibidutunga tubeho.”
5:3 Kandi abandi baravugaga bati “Amasambu yacu n'inzabibu zacu n'amazu yacu twabitanze ho ingwate, dufite inzara reka tujye guhaha.”
5:4 Kandi n'abandi baravugaga bati “Twagujije ifeza z'umusoro w'umwami dutanze amasambu yacu n'inzabibu zacu ho ingwate.
5:5 Ariko rero twebwe na bene wacu dusangiye ubwoko, kandi abana bacu na bo bava inda imwe n'ababo. Nyamara abahungu bacu n'abakobwa bacu tubatanga ho ibiretwa, ndetse abakobwa bacu bamwe bageze mu buretwa kandi tubuze uko twagira ngo tubacungure, kuko amasambu yacu n'inzabibu zacu bifitwe n'abandi.”
5:6 Numvise kwitotomba kwabo n'amaganya yabo, ndarakara cyane.
5:7 Nuko mbateraniriza iteraniro rinini.
5:8 Ndababwira nti “Twebweho uko dushoboye twacunguye bene wacu b'Abayuda bari baraguzwe n'Abanyamahanga, none namwe murashaka kugura bene wanyu. Mbese twe twabagura tukabatunga?” Nuko baraceceka babura icyo bavuga.
5:9 Ndongera ndavuga nti “Ibyo mukora si byiza. Mbese ibikwiriye si uko mwagenda mwubaha Imana yacu, ntimwitukishe mu banzi bacu b'abanyamahanga?
5:10 Nanjye na bene data n'abagaragu banjye twabagurizaga ifeza n'ingano. None ndabinginze tubaharire imyenda batubereyemo.
5:11 Ndetse uyu munsi mubasubize amasambu yabo n'inzabibu zabo, n'inzelayo zabo n'amazu yabo, mubasubize cya gice kimwe mu ijana cy'ifeza, n'icy'ingano n'icya vino n'icy'amavuta, ibyo mwabakaga.”
5:12 Maze baravuga bati “Tuzabibasubiza kandi nta cyo tuzabaka, tuzabigenza nk'uko uvuze.”
5:13 Maze nkunkumura umwenda nari niteye ndavuga nti “Imana izakunkumure itya umuntu wese udasohoza iri sezerano, imukure mu nzu ye no ku murimo we. Uwo muntu abe ari ko akunkumurwa akamarwaho.”
5:14 Kandi uhereye igihe naherewe ubutware ngo mbe igisonga cy'umwami mu gihugu cy'u Buyuda, uhereye ku mwaka wa makumyabiri ukageza ku wa mirongo itatu n'ibiri Umwami Aritazeruzi ari ku ngoma, muri iyo myaka cumi n'ibiri, jyewe na bene data ntitwatungwaga n'amakoro y'ubusonga.
5:15 Ariko ibisonga byambanjirije kera byabereye rubanda ibirushya bibāka ibyokurya na vino, udashyizeho shekeli z'ifeza mirongo ine, ndetse n'abagaragu babo batwaza rubanda igitugu. Ariko jyewe si ko nabigenje kuko nubahaga Imana,
5:16 ahubwo nagiraga umwete wo gukora nubaka inkike kandi nta gikingi cyose twaguze, kandi n'abagaragu banjye bose bateraniraga ku murimo.
5:17 Kandi abagabo ijana na mirongo itanu bo mu Bayuda n'abatware babo bariraga ku meza yanjye, udashyizeho abo twasangiye bandi bavaga mu mahanga adukikije.
5:18 Kandi igerero ry'umunsi umwe ryabagamo inka imwe n'intama esheshatu zitoranijwe, bantekeraga n'inkoko kandi uko iminsi cumi yashiraga bazanaga vino z'amoko yose, ariko ibyo byose uko bingana sinabyakaga abantu ho ikoro ry'ubusonga, kuko abo bantu barushywaga n'uburetwa.
5:19 Mana yanjye, wibuke ibyo nakoreye aba bantu, ubinyiturire ibyiza.
6:1 Bukeye babwira Sanibalati na Tobiya, na Geshemu Umwarabu n'abandi banzi bacu yuko nubatse inkike, kandi ko nta cyuho gisigaye kuri yo nubwo nari ntarakinga inzugi ku marembo.
6:2 Nuko Sanibalati na Geshemu barantumira, ngo nze duhurire mu kirorero kimwe mu byo mu gisiza cya Ono. Ariko bashakaga kungirira nabi.
6:3 Nanjye mbatumaho intumwa ndababwira nti “Ndakora umurimo ukomeye sinashobora kumanuka, nta mpamvu yo kwica umurimo ngo manuke mbasange.”
6:4 Bantumaho batyo kane, nanjye mbasubiza ntyo.
6:5 Maze Sanibalati yongera kuntumaho umugaragu we ubwa gatanu atyo, afite urwandiko rurambuye mu ntoki ze
6:6 rwari rwanditswemo ngo
6:7 Ngo washyizeho n'abahanuzi bo kwamamaza ibyawe i Yerusalemu, ngo mu Bayuda harimo umwami. None ngwino tujye inama kuko izo nkuru batazabura kuzibwira umwami.”
6:8 Nanjye mutumaho nti “Ibyo uvuze ibyo nta byabaye, ahubwo ni wowe wabyihimbiye mu mutima wawe.”
6:9 Bose bashaka kudukangisha bibwira yuko amaboko yacu azatentebuka, umurimo ntukorwe.
6:10 Maze njya kwa Shemaya mwene Delaya mwene Mehetabēli wari ukingiranye, arambwira ati “Tubonanire ku nzu y'Imana imbere mu rusengero, dukinge inzugi z'urusengero kuko bazaza kukwica. Ni koko iri joro baraza kuza kukwica.”
6:11 Ndamusubiza nti “Ndi umugabo ungana atya nahunga? Mbese ni nde mu bo tungana wahungira mu rusengero akīkiza? Sindi bujyeyo.”
6:12 Mbyitegereje menya yuko atari Imana yamutumye, ahubwo yampanuriyeho ibyo kuko Tobiya na Sanibalati bari bamuguriye.
6:13 Icyatumye agurirwa ni ukugira ngo ankangishe, maze ninkora ntyo ngo bimbere icyaha, bahere ko bamboneho impamvu yo kumvuga nabi kugira ngo bantuke.
6:14 Mana yanjye, wibuke Tobiya na Sanibalati n'ibyo bakora ibyo uko bingana, wibuke n'umuhanuzikazi Nowadiya n'abandi bahanuzi bashaka kunkangisha.
6:15 Nuko ku munsi wa makumyabiri n'itanu w'ukwezi kwitwa Eluli inkike ziruzura, twari tumaze iminsi mirongo itanu n'ibiri tuzubaka.
6:16 Maze abanzi bacu bose babyumvise, abanyamahanga bose badukikije bakuka imitima, baca bugufi cyane barigaya kuko babonye yuko Imana yacu ari yo ikoze uwo murimo.
6:17 Muri iyo minsi imfura zo mu Bayuda zoherereza Tobiya inzandiko nyinshi, kandi iza Tobiya zikabageraho.
6:18 Mu Bayuda harimo benshi basezeranye na we kuko yari muramu wa Shekaniya mwene Ara, kandi n'umuhungu we Yehohanani yari yararongoye umukobwa wa Meshulamu mwene Berekiya.
6:19 Maze bogeza ibyo yakoze imbere yanjye, kandi bamubwira ibyanjye. Nuko Tobiya akajya yohereza inzandiko zo kunkangisha.
7:1 Bukeye inkike yuzuye maze no guteraho inzugi, ngashyiraho n'abakumirizi n'abaririmbyi n'Abalewi,
7:2 nuko mpa mwene data Hanani, na Hananiya umutware w'igihome ubutware bw'i Yerusalemu, kuko yari umuntu wo kwizerwa arusha benshi kubaha Imana.
7:3 Ndabategeka nti “Inzugi z'i Yerusalemu ntizigakingurwe hataraba ku gasusuruko, kandi nibahagarara bagikumiriye bajye bakinga inzugi, muzikomereshe ibihindizo kandi mujye mushyiraho abarinzi bo mu b'i Yerusalemu, umuntu wese mu gihe cye kandi umuntu wese yitegeye inzu ye.”
7:4 Umudugudu wari munini kandi mugari, ariko abantu bari bawurimo bari bake, n'amazu yari atarubakwa.
7:5 Hanyuma Imana yanjye inshyiramo umutima wo guteranya imfura n'abatware n'abantu, ngo babarwe uko kuvuka kwabo kwari kuri. Mbona igitabo cyanditswemo ababanje kuzamuka uko kuvuka kwari kuri, nsanga cyanditswemo ngo:
